data.description: This immaculately maintained, 2021 completed "like-new" home is the perfect mix of city & country life! With less than 15 miles from downtown Tyler, you can still have the big city life in a relaxed country setting. The home offers three bedrooms and two full baths with a split bedroom arrangement. The kitchen has a large island with breakfast/dining room and an abundance of counter & storage space. Enjoy the timeless beauty of stainless steel appliances, herringbone subway backsplash and oversized granite countertops. The living area over looks the covered outdoor patio and full privacy fenced back yard. Your primary retreat with vaulted ceiling is truly a spa-like setting with double sinks, soaking tub and separate walk in shower. The over sized laundry room and mud bench can handle any of your storage needs. Don't miss your opportunity to own this stunning home!
